history.content:
In October I submitted a Change of College Application at ESS for admission into EECS from L&S. In a previous post it was made clear that notification should have been mailed by November 30, but I still haven't received anything despite some friends' applying to other Engineering Majors already having received notification.

 

Could someone confirm that the admission notification has not yet been sent? I never got confirmation that I submitted an application (the person at ESS just took my file of documents).

I know that I should email changeofcollege@berkeley.edu, which I have done, but in previous emails with this address I only get replies in a couple days. Piazza tends to give faster, more accurate and more EECS-specific information (thanks!) given that I need to know before my TeleBears appointment on December 4.

 

Thanks!
